		{
			"role": "intro",
			"text": "The approach to highlighting the female form in fashion is ever-changing. Sometimes it's about the decolletage, followed by a moment that's all derriere, and there's always the option of the full-on [naked dress](http://www.harpersbazaar.com/fashion/designers/a11157/carolina-herrera-challenges-the-naked-dress-trend/). This summer, the sensual body part to display is no doubt the leg. Thigh-high slits have been showcasing well-toned stems since May. See some well-heeled ladies give their best [Angelina Jolie](http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/02/27/angelina-jolie-right-leg-_n_1303865.html).",
